    show kaori tka09sa at l

    voice "KAORI_0136"
    kaori "「蠢材——！是你忘了吧——！」"

    show amane tam01sa at r

    voice "AMANE_0136"
    amane "「不是忘了，是课本擅自离家出走而已哦。」"

    voice "KAORI_0137a"
    kaori "「这是什么借口！？能骗谁啊。」"

    show amane tam03sa at r

    voice "AMANE_0137"
    amane "「啊啊嗯，开个玩笑啦。」"

