    show kaori tka03sa at sl
    show makoto tma01sa at sr
    show amane tam01sa at c
    with dissolve

    voice "MAKOTO_0015"
    makoto "「还剩１分钟。」"

    voice "KAORI_0140"
    kaori "「啊啊啊，就这次给你看了啦，快点给我写。」"

    show amane tam02sa at c

    voice "AMANE_0140"
